cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically with the problem of depth and pose estimation using CNNs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics and motion estimation, which suggests the category cs.RO (Robotics). The use of machine learning techniques for reconstruction and prediction indicates the category cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of neural networks for prediction, which suggests the category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves the estimation of 3D structure, which suggests the category cs.GR (Graphics).
